name: The Hundreds 'Muted Adam' Tee - Navy
description:
The Hundreds 'Muted Adam' Tee - Navy

Adam Bomb is far from being muted and understated, but we gave it the old school try this season.  The Muted Adam is a subtle approach to the Adam Bomb with graphic colors that blend effortlessly into the color of the tee.  Look for the muted Adam Bomb graphic to be paired with a Solid Bomb logo on the top back.

name: King Apparel 'Warriors' Snapback - Dark Grey
description:
King Apparel 'Warriors' Snapback - Dark Grey

Our Warriors line killed it when we released the bonus hats a few seasons ago, and now weve got a whole range lined up with our best colourways and fabric choices yet

Limited edition Starter collaboration Snapback cap. The first UK brand with the coveted Starter Black Label premium affiliation

The King Starter caps are unique in that they are still produced in the original Starter factory, retain the low profile shape and do not come with stickers and holograms to preserve their authentic feel and the heritage of the old school Starter brand

Dark grey tweed crown topped with a dark grey tweed button and eyelets. Black King Warriors logo 3D embroidery on the front with dark brown leather peak

Black Starter logo on the rear with black leather strap adjuster with blue King woven label

description:

Limited Edition 5-panel camp cap. This is not your average 5-panel, with premium materials used, reinforced front panel and the best fit, shape and construction bar none

One of the best hats we have produced, as it comprises of a combination of three different fabrics. Black cotton twill crown, black melange front panel and black suede peak

Black crossed line Insignia emblem on front panel, with original insignia logo featuring as a small high-density black silicone print on the bottom rear left panel

Black woven adjuster on rear with blue King woven label and customised interior Reign Supreme hat taping

name: King Apparel 'Classics Defy' Pinch Panel Snapback - Black
description:
King Apparel 'Classics Defy' Pinch Panel Snapback - Black

WAS 25 :: 15

For Kings tenth birthday year and as a response to the requests we have been inundated with, we have decided to release a selection of classic pieces that have shaped us as a brand. 

These are one offs and will never be repeated

King branded snapback cap. Made on the same production line as our Starter branded hats and carries the exact same low profile block, shape and construction. No compromise on quality!

Made in the classic pinch panel construction, with the front panel middle seam running just halfway down the front

Black hat topped with matching buttons and eyelets. Classic Defy paint drip logo embroidered on the front and running down onto the peak

Grey/white Reign Supreme flag embroidery on right panel with red snap adjuster and blue King woven label

Customised interior Reign Supreme hat taping

Heather grey cotton pocket on left chest with camo printed nylon top edging and luxury embossed leather King label on the bottom left of t-shirt

Comes complete with customised neck taping as well as tonal navy Reign Supreme script embroidery on right sleeve
Charcoal grey printed King shield logo on rear bottom left

2x2 ribbed collar, cuffs and waist with cyan blue King woven side seam label on bottom left seam. Crews come complete with cyan blue customised neck taping and size label

Pick it up with the Krest Select Starter Snapback of the same colours or wear as a stand-alone piece
